prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card, dreamy fantasy art style. The scene is a surreal and magical snowy mountain peak under a pastel twilight sky with soft, glowing stars. In the center, cartoon-illustrated versions of Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo are comically snowboarding down a slope. Jordan, wearing his navy t-shirt, is on a snowboard cleverly designed to look like a giant piece of marbled wagyu steak. Lao Lao, in her white zip-up top, is right beside him, joyfully riding a snowboard that looks like a giant salmon nigiri sushi roll. They both have big, happy, laughing expressions. The snowy landscape is creatively composed of their favorite things: the "trees" are actually giant chopsticks sticking out of the snow, adorned with glowing Chinese lanterns. Instead of rocks, there are oversized dumplings and siu mai dotting the mountainside. Floating whimsically in the background are glowing, ethereal lines of binary code (0s and 1s) that drift like gentle snowflakes. The overall color palette is a mix of soft pastels, magical glowing highlights, and vibrant food colors, creating a lighthearted, ethereal, and humorous atmosphere. Centered in the middle of the sky is the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan!" written in a beautiful, readable, glowing handwritten cursive script.
